text: Phankham Viphavanh (; born 14 April 1951) is a Laotian politician. In 2021, he became the Prime Minister of Laos. He is a member of Politburo. He is the Executive Committee of the Lao People's Revolutionary Party. He was the Vice President of Laos from 2016 until 2021. ==References== Category:Living people Category:1951 births Category:Prime Ministers of Laos Category:Vice presidents of Laos Category:Recipients of the Order of the Rising Sun
